        <p>The collection (donor no. <num encodinganalog="541$e" type="donor">3584</num>) was the gift of Mrs. Roy D. Chapin and other members of the Chapin family. The bulk of the collection came to the library in 1940; other smaller additions came throughout the 1940s and 1950s.</p>
